snippet.title: Inglorious | Release Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Inglorious will be available in the Playstation Store on November 7th of 2018!

Inglorious is a Dungeon Crawler Competitive game exclusive for PS4. Compete against your friends in the Local Multiplayer Splitscreen mode to see who is the best champion!
